Samsung May Use More Advanced 8th Generation Technology in China LCD Plant

-- B y   J u n   Y a n g
-- 
2011-10-12T00:51:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/samsung-may-use-more-advanced-8th-generation-technology-in-china-lcd-plant.html
Samsung Electronics Co. is
considering using so-called eighth-generation technology in its
planned liquid-crystal display plant in  China , Nam Ki Yung, a
Seoul-based spokesman for Samsung, said by phone today. The
company initially planned to use the 7.5-generation standard.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jun Yang in Seoul at 
